title: Launcher Won't Load! HELP!
body: I click the League of Legends icon on my desktop and the "League Of Legends" logo pops up but nothing happens. The launcher itself won't show up and i don't know how to fix it. Any suggestions aynone?

replies.body: Your patcher is trying to launch but some setting is blocking it from happening.  Go over our [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to get this fixed up and access restored!  Let me know if you have any questions.
